Maintainer: Stephen Balogun <stephentaiyebalogun@gmail.com>
Description: Performs data quality checks using the standard quality metrics on patient-level line-lists downloaded from the NDR
      or similar platforms. Currenlty, it supports the Recency and Mortality Surveillance line-lists.
